	"system": {
		"description": "<p>White Flames are as bright as the sun. Once per turn, when you inflict fire damage to a target, you can force it to make a Constitution Saving Throw (Spell save DC) or be [[/condition id=blinded]] until the end of its next turn. You can only use this on one target, even if you inflicted fire damage to more than one creature.</p><p>You can use this ability a number of times equal to your Constitution modifier per Long Rest.</p>",
